## Problems
1. **Hard-gate (minor, do NOT rebuild): en dash in page `<title>` separator.** Titles render `Maryland Driveway Restore &#8211; Premium driveway restoration...`; `&#8211;` is an en dash, banned everywhere by gate #5 (evaluator-enforced), and it is on every page (WP/Rank Math default separator, not authored prose). One-line config fix: add `add_filter('document_title_separator', fn()=>'|');` to the theme `functions.php` on the host mount, or set Rank Math's title-separator option. Deploy/builder should apply this before final eval; not worth a full demo-builder loop for one character.

